data.description: Beautiful 5 bed/3 bath stunner in the highly desirable Wescott Plantation and DD2 schools. NEW Roof 2022. This home was renovated and updated in 2020.  Large .27 acre lot on a cul-de-sac with a large fenced in backyard backed to woods. Home has a downstairs bedroom and full bath perfect for guests or family. Spacious, eat-in kitchen boasts granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. All solid surface flooring downstairs, except for the bedroom, that consists of laminate wood and tile. Oversized owner's suite upstairs features a tray ceiling, walk-in closet and a separate sitting area. The owner's bath features dual vanities, and a large garden tub and separate shower. Large loft space upstairs perfect for play area, or media. 3 additional bedrooms and full bath complete upstairs.Large sunroom on the back of this home opens to recently added decking and huge fenced backyard. Private backyard with gate to access woods behind this beautiful home.
